\c 13
\s Shoko raJehovha pamusoro peBhabhironi
\p
\v 1 Mutoro weBhabhironi Isaya mwanakomana waAmosi waakaona.
\p
\v 2 Simudzai mureza pagomo riri bani; simudzirai inzwi kwavari, ninirai ruoko, kuti vapinde pamasuwo evanoremekedzwakuru.
\v 3 Ndakaraira vatsvene vangu, ndakadana mhare dzangu nokuda kokutsamwa kwangu, ivo varume vangu vanofara vachizvikudza.
\v 4 Inzwai kutinhira pamakomo, kwakaita sokwavanhu vazhinji Kutinhira kweungano dzoushe kwamarudzi akaungana pamwe chete! Jehovha wehondo wogadzira hondo kundorwa.
\v 5 Vanobva kunyika iri kure, kumugumo wedenga, iye Jehovha nenhumbi dzake dzokurwa dzeshungu dzake, kuti aparadze nyika yese.
\p
\v 6 Chemai, nokuti zuva raJehovha riri pedo; rinosvika sokuparadza kunobva kuna Wemasimbaose.
\v 7 Saka maoko ese achashayiwa simba, nomoyo umwe neumwe wavanhu uchanyauka;
\v 8 vachavhunduka; vachabatwa nokurwadziwa namatambudziko; vacharwadziwa somukadzi anosununguka; vachatarisana vachashamiswa; zviso zvavo zvichafanana nezviso zvomoto.
\v 9 Tarirai, zuva raJehovha rinouya, rinotyisa, rine hasha nokutsamwa kukuru, kuti ashandure nyika iite dongo, nokuparadza vatadzi vayo vabvemo.
\v 10 Nokuti nyeredzi dzokudenga, namapoka adzo, hadzingaratidzi chiedza chadzo; zuva richasvibiswa pakubuda kwaro, uye mwedzi haungavhenekeri nechiedza chawo.
\v 11 Ndicharova nyika nokuda kokushata kwayo, navakaipa nokuda kwezvakaipa zvavo; ndichagumisa manyawi avanozvikudza, nokuwisira pasi kudada kwavanotyisa.
\v 12 Vanhu ndichavaita vashoma kupfuura goridhe rakaisvonaka, iye munhu kupfuura goridhe dzvene reOfiri.
\v 13 Saka ndichadederesa denga, nyika ichazununguswa ibve panzvimbo yayo, nehasha dzaJehovha wehondo, napazuva rokutsamwa kwake kukuru.
\v 14 Zvino semhara inovhimwa, uye sezvipfuwo zvisina unozviunganidza, saizvozvo munhu umwe neumwe achadzokera kurudzi rwake, umwe neumwe achatizira kunyika yake.
\v 15 Umwe neumwe anowanikwa, achabayiwa; umwe neumwe anobatwa, achaurawa nomunondo.
\v 16 Vacheche vavo vacharoverwa pasi pamberi pavo, dzimba dzavo dzichapambiwa, vakadzi vavo vachachinyiwa.
\v 17 Tarirai, ndichavamutsira vaMedhiya, vasingarangariri sirivha, kunyange goridhe havaifariri.
\v 18 Uta hwavo huchawisira pasi majaya avo, havangavi netsitsi nezvibereko zvechizvaro; ziso ravo haringadariki vana.
\p
\v 19 Zvino Bhabhironi, rine mbiri paushe hwese, raizvikudza VaKaradhiya pamusoro pokunaka kwaro, richaita sapanguva yakaparadza Mwari Sodhoma neGomora.
\v 20 Haringatongogarwi navanhu, hakuna vangatongogaramo kusvikira kumarudzi namarudzi; kunyange nomuArabhiya haangadziki tende rakemo, navafudzi havangavatisi mapoka avopo.
\v 21 Asi zvikara zvomusango zvichavatamo; dzimba dzavo dzichazara nezvinorira; mhou dzichagaramo, nemweya yakaipa ichatambapo.
\v 22 Mapere acharira munhare dzavo, namakava mudzimba dzamadzimambo dzaifadza; nguva yaro yaswedera pedo, mazuva aro haangawedzerwi.
